MusicTanspose APP ,best tool to pitch shift a song and tempo adjusting.

1. Support common audio formats (mp3, m4a, wav, tiff, flac, etc.) and video formats (mp4, mov, avi, mpg, etc.);
2. pitch shift , support color auxiliary prompt (green, orange, red, respectively, to indicate the impact of the change of key on the sound quality);
3. speed adjustment to multiply the speed display, while showing the beat speed (BPM);
4. independent adjustment of modulation and speed change, do not affect each other ;
5. Support multiple formats for export;



Why do I need MusicTanspose ?

Adjusting the tuning and speed of music and songs is a common problem in music learning, which can be done by professional software, but the operation is tedious and inconvenient. Music up/down is a tool to solve this problem.



About purchase:

1. Once purchased, lifetime validity;

2. MusicTanspose  do not depend on the cloud function, do not worry about the software is not available due to network and other reasons;



About the difference between the lite version and the full version:

In addition to the lite version and export file length restrictions, other features are the same, there will not be any differences.



About how to import files:

1. APP has how to import files from common APP to Music Elevation APP. 2;
2. Other APPs can generally share files into Music Elevation APP through the sharing function;
3. Support AirDrop, you can also send audio or video files via AirDrop from your Apple computer or iPhone or iPad, and then select "Music Elevation" APP to receive the files;



Some common problems and feedback:

1. When importing files, it shows that the files are not legal?

   If you are prompted that the file is not legal, you need to check if your file is corrupted and try again. You can also convert the file format to a common format and then import it.

2. When I try to listen to it, it will not work after processing the circle?

   This is most likely a file compatibility issue, so we suggest you convert the file to another format and try again. If that doesn't work, you can send the file to yueyin.music@foxmail.com and we will do our best to check the cause and release a fix as soon as possible.

   Any questions can be sent to yueyin.music@foxmail.com, or you can ask via wechat: allhealthyand.

